title: Alpha Sydney Looking for Analyst
body:
Alpha Sydney is a growing organisation with high tier players who want personal development on a consistent basis. The objective is to qualify to the OPL in split 2 of 2016, with an aggressive player and team development schedule for the next 6 months. If you are interested please add **ASYD Doss **on the league client and to find out more visit our website on:
http://alphasydney.gg/2015/10/27/alpha-sydney-lol-is-currently-looking-for-an-analyst/
